step-1
-------- 
	-> analyse database table designe based on requirment
	
		-> TABLE-1 PLAN_CATEGORY
			->CATEGORY_ID		INTEGER
			->CATEGORY_NAME		VARCHAR
			->ACTIVE_SW			VARCHAR	
			->CREATED_DATE		VARCHAR
			->UPDATED_DATE		VARCHAR
			->CREATED_BY		VARCHAR
			->UPDATED_BY		VARCHAR	
			
		-> TABLE-2 PLAN
			->PLAN_ID			INTEGER
			->PLAN_NAME			VARCHAR
			->PLAN_START_DATE	VARCHAR
			->PLAN_END_DATE		VARCHAR
			->CREATED_DATE		VARHCAR
			->UPDATED_DATE		-"-
			->CREATED_BY		-"-
			->UPDATED_BY		-"-
			
